                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200217-140-off817 t18200217-140-cd818"></join>, one watch, value 2 l.; one piece of ribbon, value 1 d., and one watch-key, value 1 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200217-140-victim1360" type="victimName">
